---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Structured Data for AI Search | Rank4AI" description="How structured data and schema markup drive AI search visibility. Content with proper schema has 2.5x higher citation chance.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Learn', href: '/learn/' },
      { label: 'Guides', href: '/learn/guides/' },
      { label: 'Structured Data For Ai' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Structured Data for AI Search</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Content with proper schema markup has a 2.5x higher chance of appearing in AI-generated answers. Structured data is the machine-readable layer that tells AI platforms exactly what your business is and how it connects to the wider web.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">In our UK testing, 44% of SME websites have no Organisation schema. AI systems cannot identify who they are from structured data. This is one of the easiest gaps to close.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Essential Schema Types for AI Visibility</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Organization + sameAs</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Anchors the entity and connects every ecosystem signal back to the canonical source. The sameAs array links to social profiles, directories, and verification platforms.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">LocalBusiness</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Address, opening hours, contact details. Essential for location-based AI recommendations.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">FAQPage</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">The single most impactful schema type for AI search. Pages with FAQ schema are directly extractable by AI platforms as structured Q&A pairs.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Article + author</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Attributes content to a specific person and organisation. AI platforms use author signals to evaluate expertise.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">BreadcrumbList</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Helps AI understand site hierarchy and topic relationships. Every content page should have breadcrumbs.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
